extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em Record Shack], a simple inventory website for your favourite vinyl records.

  h1 Music Database

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The library has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Records:] !{data[0]}
      li #[strong Artists:] !{data[1]}
      li #[strong Labels:] !{data[2]}
      li #[strong Genres:] !{data[3]}
      li #[strong Formats:] !{data[4]}